stream of consciousness what should write about am supposed to have some kind of direction or am supposed to write exactly what thinking this feels like very strange assignment for homework seems that have faith and have fun life is funny thing one minute your there and gone the next is like louie the lug mcgurg for example he died tragically at what happened somebody stepped on his fingers and is lot peoples garbage talk you have to read maybe is not no idea what is this screen is really weird how come only three lines have popped up been writing for minutes is this some kind of ploy so we can not see what we have written can not believe that only thought about that now in fact just noticed that only this much was on the screen very very interesting getting tired of typing waiting for relaxing to write something without having go back and proofread seems like you are an expert typer actually anyway now my minutes are up so have faith and have fun if you read this give me an even though does not matter this completion grade stuff is amazing all my classes should do it

here sitting in the computer lab trying to track my thoughts thinking that shouldnt worry about what to think not exactly sure why this assignment is necessary but then again no psychologist whoa change in thought now thinking of england and of how wish could go there to see the sights and see close friend who lives there now sad because this reminds me of princess diana and of what wonderful woman she was was truly saddened when heard she died she was on of those people that you dream of meeting some day even if you are only around her for moment she was the type of person that could make your whole year just by smiling at you this sadness takes me to other places now simultaneously thinking of close friend of mine who is clinically depressed and of old friend of the family who was homosexual and died this year of aids christian and strong christian beliefs but when tragedy strikes those you love the most there is wonder and doubt involving supposed loving god sometimes praise god for the things he does but other times you ask yourself why always been dreamer setting my goals high but sometimes wonder if what want to do with my life is right or if god wanted me to go off and become minister life is never simple but just try to roll with the punches minister of mine once said that some people build up barriers around themselves in order not to get hurt they try to experience the least amount of pain as possible by blocking themselves out but then he said that these same people cannot experience love very much at the same time as protecting themselves from pain they are limiting themselves to lesser degree of love then is possible want to be one of the people who can experience love greatly but in reality been hurt before and there are definite walls to protect myself from that kind of pain again whenever you go on date and you are nervous everyone says just be yourself think that is huge crock of shit multi faceted person do not even know what being myself would be is that the self that you express outwardly where in my case jovial and make people laugh or is that the self inside that has deep emotions and is very very sensitive and sometimes insecure while also being loving and caring sometimes feel like all of this love stored up inside of me and no one to give to try not to dwell in these places for any significannot amount of time think io like who but is just that really havent figured that out completely yet at first didnt know what to write but now glad we did this assignment is good to get your feelings out from inside when you do not want to tell anyone and you do not have diary bye-bye

why does this keep going to the left instead of down space at the end of each line prof pennebaker as sit in this library cannot help but notice the pleasure get from the quietness is the same feeling get from sitting in park or on golfcourse perhaps even in bookstore the quietness provides my mind with an escape from the everyday world of horns traffic jams and yelling from this feeling my mind seems to work on smoother track with less obstacles to overcome before can finish complete thought if the world was in complete silence at all times or perhaps even if were deaf believe would be wiser and would be able to formulate thoughts easier does this mean that deaf people actually have an easier time getting by in the world or is their inability to communicate too much of burden maybe this is whats wrong with todays world communication lines are so mixed up due to language barriers and different types of slang that the world is like one large deaf fishbowl in that case deaf people would have an easier everyday life because they would be minus the struggles we all go through with communication if communication were an easy things and we all saw eye-to-eye on all issues achieving things such as world peace business agreements and compromises would be no big deal where did the communication lines go wrong why did humanity branch out into hundreds of different languages and tongues when one universal language could have eliminated so many problems the answer to that will most likely never be found this girl sitting to my right is awfully attractive but cannot muscle up the courage to talk to her is once again the problem of communication or does this have to do purely with lack of courage would like to think is communication problem but that would probably be just lame excuse for not talking to her of course is lack of courage although know she will not bite my head off slap me ignore me or flat out dis me still am too much of coward to begin conversation with her what if she knew what was thinking right now would she be flattered embarrassed insulted or just flat out shocked guess ill never know unless ask her we both know that is not going to happen because weve already established that acting like coward right now no big deal there are plenty of fish in the sea wow cannot believe how fast twenty minutes just went writing without structure is lot more enjoyable then writing with and as they say time flies when youre having fun
